---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Welcome to Astro.">
  <main class="flex flex-col gap-10 mt-10">
    <h1 class="text-center text-4xl font-bold p-5 text-very-dark-cyan">
      Build The Community Your Fans Will Love
    </h1>
    <p class="text-center lg:w-1/3 md:w-1/2 m-auto p-5 text-very-dark-cyan">
      Huddle re-imagines the way we build communities. You have a voice, but so
      does your audience. Create connections with your users as you engage in
      genuine discussion.
    </p>
    <button
      class="bg-primary-pink m-auto px-10 py-2 rounded-xl text-white hover:bg-light-pink duration-500 shadow-lg"
      >Get Started For Free</button
    >
    <img
      src="/images/light-pink.svg"
      alt="imagen-section"
      width="1016"
      class="m-auto p-5"
    />
    <section
      class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-20 md:justify-evenly p-5"
    >
      <div>
        <img src="/images/icon-communities.svg" alt="" width="35" />
        <p class="text-6xl font-bold text-very-dark-cyan">1.4k+</p>
        <p class="text-center text-very-dark-cyan">Communities Formed</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img src="images/icon-messages.svg" alt="" width="25" />
        <p class="text-6xl font-bold text-very-dark-cyan">2.7m+</p>
        <p class="text-center text-very-dark-cyan">Messages Sent</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section>
      <img src="/images/bg-section-top-desktop-1.svg " alt="" class="w-full" />
      <div class="bg-very-pale-blue p-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row py-20">
          <div class="m-auto">
            <h3
              class="my-10 text-2xl md:text-6xl font-semibold text-very-dark-cyan text-center md:text-start"
            >
              Grow Together
            </h3>
            <p
              class="text-very-dark-cyan lg:m-auto md:text-xl text-center md:text-start"
            >
              Generate meaningful discussions with your audience and build a
              strong, loyal community. Think of the insightful conversations you
              miss out on with a feedback form.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <img
              src="/images/illustration-grow-together.svg"
              alt=""
              class="md:px-10 lg:m-auto"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img
        src="/images/bg-section-bottom-desktop-2.svg"
        alt=""
        class="w-full"
      />
    </section>
    <section>
      <div class="p-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row py-20">
          <div>
            <img
              src="/images/illustration-flowing-conversation.svg"
              alt=""
              class="md:px-10 lg:m-auto"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="m-auto">
            <h3
              class="my-10 text-2xl md:text-6xl font-semibold text-very-dark-cyan text-center"
            >
              Flowing Conversations
            </h3>
            <p class="text-very-dark-cyan lg:m-auto md:text-xl text-center">
              You wouldn't paginate a conversation in real life, so why do it
              online? Our threads have just-in-time loading for a more natural
              flow.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section>
      <img src="/images/bg-section-top-desktop-1.svg " alt="" class="w-full" />
      <div class="bg-very-pale-blue p-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row py-20">
          <div class="m-auto">
            <h3
              class="my-10 text-2xl md:text-6xl font-semibold text-very-dark-cyan text-center md:text-start"
            >
              Your Users
            </h3>
            <p
              class="text-very-dark-cyan lg:m-auto md:text-xl text-center md:text-start"
            >
              It takes no time at all to integrate Huddle with your app's
              authentication solution. This means, once signed in to your app,
              your users can start chatting immediately.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <img
              src="/images/illustration-your-users.svg"
              alt=""
              class="md:px-10 lg:m-auto"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img
        src="/images/bg-section-bottom-desktop-2.svg"
        alt=""
        class="w-full"
      />
    </section>
    <h3 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold">
      Ready To Build Your Community?
    </h3>
    <button
      class="bg-primary-pink m-auto px-10 py-2 rounded-xl text-white hover:bg-light-pink duration-500 shadow-lg"
      >Get Started For Free</button
    >
  </main>
</Layout>
